is a very dangerous position to put yourself in

00:00:11.842 --> 00:00:15.041
and it really really really does relies on your partner

00:00:15.042 --> 00:00:17.881
their ego and their sense of power dynamics

00:00:17.882 --> 00:00:19.961
catch you up to speed about Kyle and Amanda

00:00:19.962 --> 00:00:21.321
Kyle started his own company

00:00:21.322 --> 00:00:24.281
Lover Boy and as that company started game momentum

