he asked his then fiance

00:00:26.042 --> 00:00:30.321
now wife to quit her job to come help him full time at Loverboy

00:00:30.322 --> 00:00:30.681
she now

00:00:30.682 --> 00:00:34.201
I believe is the director or creative director or the director of marketing

00:00:34.202 --> 00:00:35.601
maybe both however

